title: Top 10 Rookies of the year
itunes:title: Top 10 Rookies of the year
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling,  & Gregg Rosenthal – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL including the latest on the Jaguars' search for a new head coach, and Bill O’Brien announcing that Tom Savage will start at quarterback for the Texans in week 16. Then, the heroes break down their top 10 rookies of 2016 before diving into Marc’s latest long-form piece: “Calling the Game.”

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
